github-fixup - GitHub Fixup Commits

USAGE:
    github-fixup

DESCRIPTION:
    Create fixup commits across all GitHub repositories and force push
    changes using iteration logic.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-github-commits NUM
        Number of commits to fixup

    -conf-github-commit-message MESSAGE
        Commit message for fixup

    -conf-github-git-projects-path PATH
        Path containing git projects

EXAMPLES:
    github-fixup
